# Anthropic Service Level Agreement (SLA)

## Overview
This document outlines the Service Level Agreement between Liaison Keyboard and Anthropic for access to Claude AI models used in reply generation.

## Service Description
Anthropic provides access to:
- Claude AI models (including Claude Sonnet 4) via API
- Model inference and text generation
- Safety and alignment features
- Usage monitoring and reporting

## Service Commitments

### Uptime/Availability
- **Monthly Uptime Percentage:** 99.9% for API availability
- **Measurement:** Calculated monthly as (Total Minutes - Downtime Minutes) / Total Minutes
- **Downtime Definition:** Inability to successfully invoke the API for >5 consecutive minutes

### Performance
- **API Response Time:** 95% of requests processed within 3 seconds (time to first token)
- **Generation Speed:** Variable based on model and prompt complexity
- **Success Rate:** 99.5% of valid API requests return successful responses

### Support
- **Response Times:**
  - Critical (Production down): 30 minutes
  - High (Major feature impaired): 2 business hours
  - Normal (General inquiry): 8 business hours
- **Availability:** 24/7 support via email and ticket system
- **Documentation:** Comprehensive API documentation available

## Remedies
### Service Credits
If Anthropic fails to meet the Monthly Uptime Percentage:
- 95.0% ≤ Uptime < 99.0%: 10% credit of monthly fees
- 90.0% ≤ Uptime < 95.0%: 25% credit of monthly fees
- Uptime < 90.0%: 100% credit of monthly fees

### Claim Procedure
1. Customer must submit credit claim within 30 days of the end of the month in which the SLA violation occurred
2. Claims submitted via: https://anthropic.com/contact
3. Anthropic will respond within 5 business days
4. Approved credits applied to next invoice

## Exclusions
SLA does not apply to:
- Issues caused by Customer's equipment, software, or third-party services
- Scheduled maintenance (with ≥ 24 hours notice)
- Force majeure events
- Issues arising from Customer's violation of terms
- Rate limiting due to Customer exceeding API limits
- Invalid requests or malformed prompts
- Network issues outside of Anthropic's control

## Contact Information
- **Anthropic Support:** https://anthropic.com/contact
- **Emergency:** Priority email support for Critical issues
- **Account Manager:** [To be assigned]
- **Legal/Contracts:** legal@anthropic.com

## Review and Amendment
This SLA shall be reviewed annually or upon significant service changes. Amendments require written agreement from both parties.

